---
title: Dutch Pork Filet with Orange-Dijon Sauce Top recipes from HelloFresh markets around the world
description: In honor of the summer games, we’re going global with this gold medal winner from HF in the Netherlands! You’ll whip up a delectable pan sauce with fresh orange juice, tangy Dijon mustard, and a touch of butter and brown sugar, then spoon it over juicy pork filets. Sweet roasted carrots and buttery mashed potatoes round it all out, along with a sprinkle of nutty almonds for crunchy contrast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/667075fb98f15bd5272cfb10-b965bbf6.jpeg
