  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 530 mg
time required: 40 minutes
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/dutch-pork-filet-with-orange-dijon-sauce-667075fb98f15bd5272cfb10
author: Sara Heilman
